title: We Can't Believe The Hardcore Marriage Rules This Couple Has
description:
We understand that marriage is hard work, and sometimes you two have to come to certain agreements to make the marriage work. In this case, this young couple has a list of strict rules for their marriage.
Are these rules out of control or reasonable? We discuss.
